    <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, субстратного (кавказского) происхождения. Сближается с <mentioned
            xml:lang="sva"><lang/><w>mačʼičʼ</w><gloss><q>бородавка</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
            ><lang/><w>mucʼukʼi</w><gloss><q>чирей</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>прыщ</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="x-crc"
                ><lang/><w>xa-mzikie</w><gloss><q>бородавка</q></gloss></mentioned> (? <bibl><ref
                target="#ref_Люлье"/></bibl>). Звуковой тип %ibsk%i мог получиться в результате
        метатезы из %ikbs%i; ср. д. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼubus"/> ‘шишка’, <mentioned
            xml:lang=""><lang/><w>gubus</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang=""
                    ><w>gubuz</w><gloss><q>бородавка</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">It is probably of a substrate (Caucasian) origin. It gets close to
            <mentioned xml:lang="sva"><lang/><w>mačʼičʼ</w><gloss><q>wart</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
            ><lang/><w>mucʼukʼi</w><gloss><q>furuncle</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>pimple</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned
            xml:lang="x-crc"><lang/><w>xa-mzikie</w><gloss><q>wart</q></gloss></mentioned> (?
                <bibl><ref target="#ref_Люлье"/></bibl>). Sound %ibsk%i could result from the
        metathesis from %ikbs%i; cf. Digor <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼubus"/> ‘cone’,
            <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/><w>gubus</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang=""
                ><w>gubuz</w><gloss><q>wart</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym>
</entry>
